title: #92Noon! Boudreau/Patterson/Gleeman/Birk/Softy!
description: Wild coach Bruce Boudreau kicks off the show, Vikings DLine coach Andre Patterson,"Niners Du Nord" is all about the Niners and the game Saturday, Gleeman in studio, Birk Bit for a couple segments, then Softy from Seattle to close!
